            <title><![CDATA[Falcom’s unannounced game for 2026 to be revealed in February]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/02/falcoms-unannounced-game-for-2026-to-be-revealed-in-february</link>
            <guid>1422436</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [767 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a>‘s <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/12/falcom-developing-unannounced-trails-and-ys-games-additional-new-title-due-out-in-2026">unannounced new title due out in 2026</a> will be revealed in February, Falcom president Toshihiro Kondo said in an interview at Taipei Game Show 2026. <span id="more-1023007"></span></p><p>“Regarding 2026, as mentioned in the question, we have already decided to release two new titles,” Kondo told <a href="https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=299429" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gamer.com.tw</a>, referring to <em><a title="Games > Trails in the Sky 2nd Chapter [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/trails-in-the-sky-2nd-chapter">Trails in the Sky 2nd Chapter</a></em> and an unannounced game. “That’s something we haven’t done in several decades. We are fairly confident about that in terms of development progress, and are currently at a stage where this goal appears quite feasible.</p><p>“As for the second title aside from <i>Trails in the Sky 2nd Chapter</i>, we are planning a major announcement next month [in February]. We intend to make a big reveal.</p><p>“This year also marks Falcom’s 45th anniversary, and we hope to build hype around this milestone by announcing stuff in a good pace. So we kindly ask everyone to be patient and stay tuned for further updates.”</p><p>While Falcom has not made any direct statements about what its unannounced title for 2026, a <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/12/games-industry-new-year-2026-cards-and-messages" target="_blank" rel="noopener">New Year’s greeting card</a> suggests it will be the <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/03/tokyo-xanadu-new-project-announced-for-console">2024-announced</a> <em><a title="Games > Tokyo Xanadu New Project [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tokyo-xanadu-new-project">Tokyo Xanadu New Project</a></em>, which is set in Kyoto.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/02/falcoms-unannounced-game-for-2026-to-be-revealed-in-february]]></content:encoded>
            <dc:creator>invalid@example.com (ResetEra_Newsbot</dc:creator>
